About: In 2022 the highly anticipated and long-awaited Worlds Collide Tour kicked off. Few collaborations in Within Temptation’s career have ignited as much anticipation as their co-headlining tour with Evanescence, after it being postponed four times due to COVID. As soon as the world reopened, the Worlds Collide Tour finally took place. During this tour, Within Temptation played two sold-out shows in their home country at Ziggo Dome in Amsterdam (NL). They were their first-ever headlining shows in Ziggo Dome and a total of 30.000 fans were there to witness. Now, fans get to relive the adrenaline-pumping excitement of the Worlds Collide Tour from the comfort of their home with the first show in Ziggo Dome, Amsterdam (NL) on November 30, 2022, now being available on Blu-ray-DVD digipack.
